OL,3,CHundreds of jobs under threat as food
OL,4,Cgroup set to close factory
OL,6,FAround 750 jobs are under threat after
OL,7,Ffood group Bakkavor announced it could
OL,8,Fclose its factory.
OL,10,FThe company published a statement on
OL,11,Fthe stock market saying its Wigan meal
OL,12,Fproduction facility, at Ince, was
OL,13,F"unsustainable with low margin
OL,14,Fbusiness in a factory that needs
OL,15,Fsignificant investment".
OL,17,FThe Iceland-headquartered company owns
OL,18,F20 other factories across the UK,
OL,19,Fincluding in Crewe and Nantwich, as
OL,20,Fwell as the one on Manchester Road at
OL,21,FInce-in-Makerfield.
