OL,3,CHundreds of jobs under threat as food
OL,4,Cgroup set to close factory
OL,6,F"This has resulted in the difficult
OL,7,Fbut necessary decision to announce the
OL,8,Fpotential closure of this site, with
OL,9,Fconsultation to commence at the end of
OL,10,FSeptember 2024," it said.
OL,12,FThe company said it planned to offer
OL,13,Fcolleagues 'alternative roles wherever
OL,14,Fpossible'.
OL,16,F"We will also be working on several
OL,17,Falternative initiatives to help
OL,18,Fcolleagues secure alternative
OL,19,Femployment opportunities in the local
OL,20,Farea."
