OL,3,CHundreds of jobs under threat as food
OL,4,Cgroup set to close factory
OL,6,FThe factory produces potatoe dishes,
OL,7,Ffreshly prepared vegetables,ready
OL,8,Fmeals and salads.
OL,10,FResponding to the news, Wigan council
OL,11,Fleader, Councillor David Molyneux,
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are deeply disappointed at
OL,13,Fthis news and we will try to support
OL,14,Fthe workforce as best we can.
OL,16,F"I have asked the council's economic
OL,17,Fteam to make contact with the company
OL,18,Fand support all those facing
OL,19,Fredundancy and their families."
